query:
INSERT INTO warehouseLocations (code, zoneId, tenantId, status, locationType, storageRule, createdAt, updatedAt) 
SELECT 'REC-SHARED-01', id, NULL, 'available', 'whole', 'multi', NOW(), NOW() 
FROM warehouseZones 
WHERE name LIKE '%Recebimento%' 
LIMIT 1;
